'''玛丽察·马丁·穆诺茨'''（Maritza Martin Munoz，{{bd|1959年|10月29日|1993年|1月18日}}），女，在[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[北劳德代尔_(佛罗里达州)|北劳德代尔]]墓地被前夫埃米利奥·努涅斯（Emilio Nuñez）枪杀。事发前努涅斯在女儿的墓前悼念，[[Ocurrió_Así|Ocurrió Así]]电视台记者英格丽德·克鲁兹（Ingrid Cruz）正在采访他<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-1993-01-19-9301040473-story.html |title=PoliceE: Man Kills Ex-Wife as Camera Rolls |first=Sallie |last=James |work=Sun-Sentinel |date=1993-01-19 |access-date=2020-06-12 |archive-date=2020-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612075649/https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-1993-01-19-9301040473-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。当电视台在拍摄努涅兹时，马丁开车前来，记者克鲁兹前往采访马丁<ref name=TelemundoVideo>{{cite av media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NZRgLIXchn0 |title=Asesinato en cementerio North Lauderdale Florida Testigo en Video vhs83 |medium=[[YouTube|YouTube]] |work=[[Telemundo|Telemundo]] |date=1993-01-18 |access-date=2020-06-05 |archive-date=2020-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122145400/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NZRgLIXchn0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。马丁和努涅兹15岁的女儿Yoandra在1992年怀孕13周时自杀身亡，努涅兹将Yoandra的死归咎于马丁。努涅斯认为女儿曾被继父虐待，并被马丁谋杀或强迫自杀<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1993-01-20/news/9301040629_1_neighbors-emilio-nunez-maritza-martin-munoz |title=Murder Suspect 'Snapped' He Blamed Ex-wife For Daughter`s Death |first1=Sallie |last1=James |first2=Luisa |last2=Yanez |work=[[Sun-Sentinel|Sun-Sentinel]] |date=1993-01-20 |access-date=2020-06-12 |archive-date=2018-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181010005724/http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1993-01-20/news/9301040629_1_neighbors-emilio-nunez-maritza-martin-munoz |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这两种说法都被调查人员驳回。Yoandra是由马丁抚养长大的，努涅兹在这期间与她没有任何联系<ref name=SunSentinel>{{cite news |url=http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/2000-01-26/news/0001260127_1_emilio-nunez-daughter-s-death-ex-wife |title=Nunez Found Guilty In Death Of Ex-wife |first=Paula |last=McMahon |work=[[Sun-Sentinel|Sun-Sentinel]] |date=2000-01-26 |access-date=2020-06-12 |archive-date=2014-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223191518/http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/2000-01-26/news/0001260127_1_emilio-nunez-daughter-s-death-ex-wife |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

克鲁兹不断敲打马丁的车窗好让她回答问题，这时努涅斯离开墓地回到他的车上。马丁随后下车记下努涅兹的车牌号，然后转身走向坟墓，完全无视克鲁兹提出的一连串问题<ref name=TelemundoVideo/>。马丁默默走向坟墓时克鲁兹仍在不断向她发问，这时努涅斯突然拿着一把9毫米[[半自動手槍|半自動手槍]]回来，朝马丁背后开枪，马丁中弹扑倒在地，努涅斯又朝她补了几枪。案发过程被摄影师录下，克鲁兹尖叫着跑向电视台的车<ref name=TelemundoVideo/>。这段影片后来被电影《[[科倫拜校園事件_(電影)|科倫拜校園事件]]》<ref>Moore, Michael "Bowling for Columbine, 2002</ref>和《[[地下影带|地下影带]]》引用。

马丁死后留下了一个18个月大的儿子<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1993-01-22/news/9301050077_1_emilio-nunez-maritza-martin-wife |title=Dead Woman`s Spouse Disputes Suspect`s Claim To Be Loving Dad |first=Sallie |last=James |work=Sun-Sentinel |date=1993-01-22 |access-date=2020-06-12 |archive-date=2018-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181012163110/http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1993-01-22/news/9301050077_1_emilio-nunez-maritza-martin-wife |dead-url=no }}</ref>。马丁她被葬在女儿旁边<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1993-01-21/news/9301040882_1_emilio-nunez-maritza-martin-munoz-yoandra|title=Man Jailed In Slaying Of Ex-wife Video-murder Suspect Caught On Bus In Texas |first=Sallie |last=James |work=Sun-Sentinel} |date=1993-01-21 |access-date=2020-06-12}}</ref>。

2000年，[[劳德代尔堡|劳德代尔堡]]陪审团裁定埃米利奥·努涅斯有罪<ref name="houston">''The Houston Chronicle'', January 26, 2000</ref>，判处无期徒刑，服刑25年后方有可能假释<ref name=SunSentinel/>。

